article_id:2834,category_name:Events,title_name:Epilogue Added to the Resplendent Refrain Raid Event Revival!,image_path:,message:<div>An epilogue has been added to the raid event revival Resplendent Refrain, which ended on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1651211999"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/86a7a59da45d7760dfe77febff813977.png"></div><div><br></div><div>You can view the epilogue by tapping the banner on the lower-left corner of the Home screen, which can be accessed from the in-game footer menu, then selecting View Quests.</div><div><br></div><div>â– Epilogue Availability</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1651212000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1651816799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Note:</div><div>The epilogue can only be viewed by players who have completed episode 5 of the event&#39;s story.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1651212000,update_time1644386824